lead_paragraph: Formula One's much-derided new qualifying format faces more criticism in Bahrain this weekend after a disappointing debut in Australia, Mercedes motorsport director Toto Wolff said on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Bahrain Qualifying Will Be Another Fail, Says Wolff
